</div>
<div type="content">
<pb facs="#facs_287"/>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l7">Eʒ iſt den ~ Schreẏbern in offem Rate geſagt worden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l8">vver hewſer oder <del rend="strikethrough">et </del>
<expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan> erb hıe kaufft darauſʒ die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l9"><expan>Teutſchenh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> hıe gült
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ der kauffer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l10">vnd verkauffer mit den cʒewgen <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
            oder mer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l11">hinauſʒ cʒum Teutſchenhawſe geen <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan>
            . vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l12">das dem cʒinſemeiſter doſelbſt ſagen / vnd den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l13">kauffer ein / vnd den verkauffer auſʒ
              <expan>Jre<ex>m</ex></expan> puch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l14">ſchreiben heiſſen / vnd <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> das
                <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l15">So ſol man <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dem kauffer erſt
                <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> kauffbrief </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l16">vnter des gerihts Jnſigel <expan>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
            laſſen / doch ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l17">bedarff man niht darein <expan>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ
            eʒ mit der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l18">
<del rend="strikethrough">St </del>
<expan>Tewtſche<ex>n</ex>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeẏ . <expan>Act<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l20">ıj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Lucie Anno etc xv<hi rend="sup">mo</hi> / <note place="inline">Abeſt  <expan>a<ex>lio</ex>modo</expan>
</note></ab>
<note place="bottomcentral">
